<Docs title="Docker Setup" description="Run Hippocampus with Docker Compose and optional CLI container workflow.">
  <h1 id="docker-setup">Docker Setup</h1>
  <p>
    The Docker setup runs three services: <code>hippocampus</code>, <code>qdrant</code>, and <code>ollama</code>.
    Data and models are persisted under the repository <code>data/</code> directory.
  </p>

  <h2 id="start-stop">Start And Stop</h2>
  <pre><code># Start all core services
npm run docker:up

# Stop and remove containers
npm run docker:down

# Tail Hippocampus logs
npm run docker:logs</code></pre>

  <h2 id="pull-models">Pull Default Models</h2>
  <pre><code>npm run docker:setup</code></pre>
  <p>
    This uses the <code>ollama-pull</code> setup profile to pull <code>phi3:mini</code> and
    <code>moondream</code> into the local Ollama volume.
  </p>

  <h2 id="run-cli-in-container">Run CLI In Container</h2>
  <pre><code># Generic pattern
npm run docker:ingest -- &lt;command&gt; [args]

# Examples
npm run docker:ingest -- ingest /uploads/notes.pdf
npm run docker:ingest -- query "memory consolidation"
npm run docker:ingest -- query-answer "Summarize the key findings"</code></pre>

  <h2 id="mounted-volumes">Mounted Volumes</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><code>./data/hippocampus:/app/data</code></li>
    <li><code>./data/models:/app/models</code></li>
    <li><code>./uploads:/app/uploads</code></li>
    <li><code>./data/piper-voices:/app/piper-voices</code></li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="important-ports">Important Ports</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><code>3001</code>: Hippocampus HTTP</li>
    <li><code>50051</code>: Hippocampus gRPC</li>
    <li><code>6333</code> and <code>6334</code>: Qdrant HTTP and gRPC</li>
    <li><code>11434</code>: Ollama API</li>
  </ul>
</Docs>
